&gt; &gt; and thus are not in a good state of mind, how come on Paranormal 
&gt; &gt; State CM was willing to believe the message given by the ghost 
via 
&gt; &gt; the box as being truth (The ghost via the box said a &quot;demon&quot; was 
&gt; &gt; holding the ghosts captive there)? 
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; I would suggest that perhaps a ghost (assuming we are talking 
about 
&gt; a 
&gt; &gt; disembodied person who remains earthbound) is not in a healthy 
&gt; state 
&gt; &gt; of mind one would consider &quot;stable,&quot; but trapped in emotional 
&gt; trauma 
&gt; &gt; of some sort. Thus, how reliable could the message of a ghost 
then 
&gt; &gt; be? ;)
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; LC
&gt; &gt; 
